{"id": "151-1722-2-4", "original": "8 . Lokuttarakathā ", "content": "8.出世間的談論"}
{"id": "151-1723-2-12", "original": "43. Katame dhammā lokuttarā? ", "content": "43.哪些法是出世間的？"}
{"id": "151-1723-13-46", "original": "Cattāro satipaṭṭhānā, cattāro sammappadhānā, cattāro iddhipādā, pañcindriyāni, pañca balāni, satta bojjhaṅgā, ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo, cattāro ariyamaggā, cattāri ca sāmaññaphalāni, nibbānañca– ime dhammā lokuttarā. ", "content": "四念住、四正勤、四神足、五根、五力、七覺支、八支聖道、四聖道、四沙門果，這些法是出世間的。"}
{"id": "151-1724-2-6", "original": "{Lokuttarā}ti kenaṭṭhena lokuttarā? ", "content": "「出世間」：以何義為出世間？"}
{"id": "151-1724-7-11", "original": "Lokaṃ tarantīti– lokuttarā. ", "content": "「他們渡世間。」為出世間；"}
{"id": "151-1724-12-16", "original": "Lokā uttarantīti– lokuttarā. ", "content": "「他們超越世間」為出世間；"}
{"id": "151-1724-17-21", "original": "Lokato uttarantīti– lokuttarā. ", "content": "「他們從世間(Lokato)超越」為出世間；"}
{"id": "151-1724-22-26", "original": "Lokamhā uttarantīti– lokuttarā. ", "content": "「他們從世間(Lokamhā)超越」為出世間；"}
{"id": "151-1724-27-31", "original": "Lokaṃ atikkamantīti– lokuttarā. ", "content": "「他們越過世間」為出世間；"}
{"id": "151-1724-32-36", "original": "Lokaṃ samatikkamantīti– lokuttarā. ", "content": "「他們渡過世間」為出世間；"}
{"id": "151-1724-37-41", "original": "Lokaṃ samatikkantāti– lokuttarā. ", "content": "「他們超過世間」為出世間；"}
{"id": "151-1724-42-46", "original": "Lokena atirekāti– lokuttarā. ", "content": "「他們以世間為多餘的」為出世間；"}
{"id": "151-1724-47-51", "original": "Lokantaṃ tarantīti– lokuttarā. ", "content": "「他們超越世間邊」為出世間；"}
